copy all files to your computer
go to directory where all files are present
give execute permission to .sh file
./filename.sh run the file
curl sS https://getcomposer.org/installer | php (run the command to download composer.phar)
php composer.phar install
copy all .php,png,vendor directory to /var/www/html location
cp *.php /var/www/html
cp *.png .var/www/html
cp -R vendor /var/www/html
in browser pubIP/index.php to open in browser
